Class PROSACRobustRangingPositionEstimator3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.position.RobustPositionEstimator<P,​RangingReading<? extends RadioSource>,​RobustRangingPositionEstimatorListener<P>>

          • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.position.PROSACRobustRangingPositionEstimator3D
  • public class PROSACRobustRangingPositionEstimator3D
extends RobustRangingPositionEstimator3D
    Robustly estimates 3D position using located radio sources and their ranging readings at unknown locations and using PROSAC algorithm to discard outliers. This kind of estimator can be used to robustly determine the 3D position of a given device by getting ranging readings at an unknown location of different radio sources whose 3D locations are known.

        public double getThreshold()
